Package: chalow
Version: 1.0-5
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Tatsuya Kinoshita <tats@debian.org>
Installed-Size: 158
Depends: perl, libjcode-pm-perl, libhtml-template-perl
Suggests: tdiary-theme
Section: web
Priority: optional
Homepage: http://chalow.org/
Description: weblog tool that converts ChangeLog to HTML
 chalow (CHAngeLog On the Web) is a weblog tool written in Perl.
 It converts ChangeLog to HTML and RSS.
 .
 chalow supports themes of design templates for tDiary weblog system.
 To use the themes of tDiary, install the tdiary-theme package.
